Driver:
(laughing)<i> I guess</i>
<i>karen ain't calling</i>
<i>the manager today.</i>

03:07.988 --> 03:09.421
Passenger:
<i>She's handling her</i>
<i>business herself.</i>

03:09.490 --> 03:11.390
Driver:
<i>Mm mm, oh!</i>
<i>She tryin' to, oh!</i>

03:11.525 --> 03:13.625
<i>Oh man, she gonna</i>
<i>crack the window!</i>

