But as it was really
a she said/she said,

15:07.173 --> 15:09.607
We just decided moving nina
would be best for everyone.

15:09.676 --> 15:10.775
Bethany:
<i> But then covid hit</i>

15:10.910 --> 15:12.176
And the accused
ended up back

15:12.178 --> 15:13.611
On the late
