Your honour,
the defence is arguing

15:22.255 --> 15:24.021
<i> That the complainant</i>
<i> attacked the accused</i>

15:24.090 --> 15:25.990
<i> Because she gave</i>
<i> her mother covid-19.</i>

15:26.059 --> 15:27.391
<i> They've made this relevant.</i>

