symptoms April 21st.

15:36.970 --> 15:39.070
Bethany:
<i> And was the accused</i>
<i> part of her team?</i>

15:39.072 --> 15:42.273
Cathy:
<i> Yes, but she'd only just</i>
<i> returned to work days earlier.</i>

15:42.275 --> 15:43.708
<i> Nina was off</i>
<i> for two weeks.</i>

15:43.777 --> 15:45.176
<i> Vacation.</i>

15:45.178 --> 15:47.445
Bethany:
<i> She took a vacation at</i>
<i> the height of the pandemic?</i>

15:47.447 --> 15:49.246
Nina said her husband
had to go out of town

15:49.282 --> 15:50.648
For a family emergency.

15:50.650 --> 15:51.683
