let that happen.

17:23.676 --> 17:24.876
Doug:
<i> Iris is right.</i>

17:25.011 --> 17:26.277
We'll settle this.

17:30.450 --> 17:31.415
Dr. Jones,

17:31.484 --> 17:33.417
Can you state your
occupation for the record?

17:33.420 --> 17:35.153
I'm the chief physician
for oakland group,

17:35.288 --> 17:36.287
The owner of oakland park,

17:36.422 --> 17:37.555
The long term care home

17:37.557 --> 17:39.490
Where the defendant worked.

17:39.526 --> 17:41.592
Bethany:
<i> Can you describe</i>
<i> the covid protocols</i>

17:41.727 --> 17:44.262
That oakland group put in
place for their facilities?

17:44.264 --> 17:45.930
The covid protocols
I put in place, uh,

17:46.065 --> 17:47.831
Across the oakland
suite of homes

