Were based in the science
available at the time.

17:50.437 --> 17:52.837
<i> Ppe, facial shields, masks,</i>

17:52.839 --> 17:54.739
Increased ventilation,
distancing.

17:54.874 --> 17:57.375
Unfortunately, with the
staff coming and going,

17:57.510 --> 17:59.577
