connections to family

18:12.192 --> 18:14.959
<i> Living in covid hotspots</i>
<i> like the preston area,</i>

18:15.561 --> 18:16.928
"hotspotters".

18:17.063 --> 18:18.996
Bethany:
<i> So you believe that</i>
<i> one of the support staff</i>

18:19.065 --> 18:20.864
Is responsible
for the outbreak?

18:21.568 --> 18:22.566
Objection. Speculation.

18:23.569 --> 18:24.869
Bethany:
<i> I have no further questions.</i>

