<i> Would you mind reading</i>

18:32.212 --> 18:34.178
<i> The highlighted</i>
<i> portion to the court?</i>

18:34.314 --> 18:37.481
Ah, it says 35% of
oakland group's employees

18:37.484 --> 18:39.216
Work across the
various facilities.

18:39.252 --> 18:40.484
Marcie:
<i> And how many employees</i>

18:40.487 --> 18:42.820
Work at the
north end halifax facility?

18:42.822 --> 18:43.954
Thirty, give or take.

18:43.990 --> 18:45.356
Marcie:
<i> And your</i>
<i> clayton park facility?</i>

18:46.325 --> 18:47.591
Thirty-six, I believe.

18:47.627 --> 18:49.193
And your bedford facility?

18:49.328 --> 18:50.761
Fifty-four.

18:50.763 --> 18:53.997
According to my quick
math that's 120 people.

18:54.033 --> 18:57.368
<i> And according to your own</i>
<i> human resources report,</i>

18:57.370 --> 18:59.303
<i> Thirty-five percent</i>
<i> of those people,</i>

18:59.372 --> 19:01.505
<i> So forty-two staff,</i>

19:01.574 --> 19:04.908
