the various facilities

19:04.944 --> 19:06.844
<i> In the midst</i>
<i> of a pandemic.</i>

19:08.114 --> 19:10.581
<i> And these numbers include</i>
<i> doctors and nurses?</i>

19:10.617 --> 19:12.049
Yes.

19:12.085 --> 19:14.785
Marcie:
<i> And do these doctors and</i>
<i> nurses work at other hospitals</i>

19:14.821 --> 19:16.921
Or other long term
care facilities?

19:16.990 --> 19:18.121
Some of them, yes.

19:18.158 --> 19:20.924
Marcie:
<i> So isn't it true</i>
<i> you have no idea</i>

19:21.060 --> 19:22.994
<i> What the source of the</i>
<i> outbreak might've been</i>

19:23.129 --> 19:24.461
At the north end facility?

19:24.497 --> 19:25.462
Objection, your honour.

19:25.498 --> 19:26.397
Judge kilcoyne:
<i> We'll continue.</i>

19:26.532 --> 19:27.598
Sit down, ms. Mayle.

19:27.600 --> 19:29.600
We acted in accordance
with the protocols

19:29.669 --> 19:31.134
Set by the government
at the time.

19:31.171 --> 19:32.703
Right, so the bare minimum.

19:33.972 --> 19:36.574
Are you currently being
sued by ms. Macaskill

19:36.709 --> 19:39.743
<i> For negligence in connection</i>
<i> with the death of her mother?</i>

19:39.779 --> 19:40.945
Bethany:
<i> Objection, your honour.</i>

19:40.947 --> 19:42.380
<i> Where is ms. Diggs</i>
<i> getting this from?</i>

19:42.515 --> 19:44.081
Did you insinuate
to ms. Macaskill

19:44.150 --> 19:45.916
During your
settlement discussions

19:45.985 --> 19:49.053
<i> That my client exposed</i>
<i> her mother to covid-19?</i>

19:49.055 --> 19:51.422
Your honour, orlando beam,

19:51.491 --> 19:53.023
Counsel for oakland park

19:53.059 --> 19:54.792
And I've instructed
dr. Jones

19:54.927 --> 19:57.361
<i> That conversations between</i>
<i> the group and ms. Macaskill</i>

19:57.363 --> 19:59.430
Are privileged communication.

19:59.499 --> 20:01.432
I'm sorry,
who are you again?

20:01.501 --> 20:02.700
Orlando bloom?

20:02.702 --> 20:03.601
Orlando beam.

20:03.670 --> 20:04.769
Okay.

20:06.172 --> 20:07.672
Members of the jury,

20:07.674 --> 20:10.140
<i> I apologize for</i>
<i> the workout today,</i>

20:10.176 --> 20:14.345
But ms. Diggs, ms. Mayle,
mr. Beam and I

20:14.414 --> 20:16.213
Will need to have a
private conversation.

20:16.216 --> 20:21.051
(tense dramatic music)

20:21.120 --> 20:22.519
Orlando:
<i> I cannot allow dr. Jones</i>

20:22.521 --> 20:25.422
To answer questions related
to ongoing litigation.

20:25.424 --> 20:27.191
Your honour, if I'm not
allowed to conduct

20:27.260 --> 20:28.925
A full cross examination

20:28.962 --> 20:31.395
Of the evidence that dr. Jones
provided then I can't-

20:31.397 --> 20:33.831
Bethany:
<i> Ms. Diggs is attempting</i>
<i> to establish some proximity-</i>

20:33.900 --> 20:35.399
Marcie:
<i> I don't have to attempt.</i>

20:35.401 --> 20:38.669
Ms. Macaskill met with
dr. Jones and mr. Beam

20:38.804 --> 20:41.405
Immediately prior to confronting
my client at her home

20:41.407 --> 20:43.140
With her small children.

20:43.142 --> 20:45.409
<i> Something happened</i>
<i> at that meeting</i>

20:45.411 --> 20:47.344
That set her off in my
client's direction.

20:47.346 --> 20:48.913
Unfortunately,
that's information

20:49.048 --> 20:51.349
Dr. Jones will be
unable to share.

20:51.351 --> 20:52.817
Judge kilcoyne:
<i> Ms. Diggs, the</i>
<i> court acknowledges</i>

20:52.952 --> 20:54.385
Solicitor-client privilege-

20:54.454 --> 20:55.886
Marcie:
<i> With respect your honour,</i>

20:55.888 --> 20:58.322
Mr. Beam has no standing
in this proceeding.

21:00.560 --> 21:02.493
Dr. Jones will not
answer any questions

21:02.628 --> 21:04.495
Related to the
ongoing litigation

21:04.497 --> 21:07.631
Between oakland park
and ms. Macaskill.

21:07.634 --> 21:09.099
Marcie:
<i> Your honour, your</i>
<i> ruling interferes</i>

21:09.135 --> 21:10.835
With my ability to
defend my client-

21:10.970 --> 21:12.103
Judge kilcoyne:
<i> Enough!</i>

21:12.105 --> 21:14.171
Move along to your
next witness.

21:14.307 --> 21:16.573
<i> Sheriff, bring the</i>
<i> jury back please.</i>

21:21.748 --> 21:23.581
Coffee
smells incredible.

