You didn't get that from
around here, did you?

21:25.585 --> 21:26.917
I know a guy.

21:26.919 --> 21:28.853
You want one?
It's high protein.

21:28.988 --> 21:29.920
Oh, for sure.

21:29.956 --> 21:33.324
(phone ringing)

21:33.459 --> 21:34.758
