so I stayed home with them.

28:42.221 --> 28:44.221
I asked cathy collins,
my supervisor,

28:44.223 --> 28:46.690
To use sick days,

28:46.692 --> 28:50.227
But the only way she'd
agree is if I took vacation.

28:50.296 --> 28:51.561
Marcie:
<i> So you did the</i>
<i> right thing,</i>

28:51.696 --> 28:54.030
