31:29.121 --> 31:30.320
Some kind of criminal.

31:32.591 --> 31:33.924
I was ashamed.

31:34.059 --> 31:37.094
Bethany:
<i> Were you ashamed</i>
<i> or selfish?</i>

31:37.229 --> 31:39.196
You just cared about what
people would say about you.

31:39.198 --> 31:40.630
No.

31:40.699 --> 31:43.133
Bethany:
<i> You didn't care you'd exposed</i>
<i> your co-workers to covid.</i>

31:43.268 --> 31:45.202
