have infected other patients

31:45.204 --> 31:46.169
At oakland park.

31:46.205 --> 31:47.137
I did.

31:47.206 --> 31:48.472
Bethany:
<i> Just like you</i>
<i> didn't care</i>

31:48.474 --> 31:50.974
When you hit ms. Macaskill
with your vehicle.

31:50.976 --> 31:53.810
I wasn't trying
to hurt her.

31:53.812 --> 31:55.946
I wasn't trying
to hurt anyone.

31:56.081 --> 31:58.047
Bethany:
<i> But you did,</i>
<i> didn't ya?</i>

31:58.083 --> 31:59.282
Objection!

31:59.351 --> 32:01.050
